description:
PowerBASIC generates the fastest machine code of all Win32-BASIC-Compilers and is even comparable (in that aspect) to programming languages like Delphi/Pascal.
Additionally, executables are very small, as PB was fully written in ASM.
It also has a very useful inline-Assembler.

Version 5 of the console compiler is the classic version of the famous compiler, still featured on the developer's site.
More description can be found at http://www.powerbasic.com/products/clCC/


